{"tid":2322531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府禁英航客機由倫敦抵港直至本月25日","createTime":"2020-12-12T11:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T12:26:55.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0b174ce6d691af4a3de0330b2e4907616e558528","tid":2322531,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:28:17.000Z","msg":"政府禁英航客機由倫敦抵港直至本月25日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564977-20201212.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564977-20201212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=64536686\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564977-20201212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=069d47cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564977-20201212.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n一班本周二由倫敦抵港的英航航班，有4名乘客感染新型肺炎，衞生署禁止英航客機於今日起至本月25日期間，由倫敦抵達本港。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署指，本周二由倫敦飛抵香港的英航BA027航班，有4名乘客感染新型肺炎，亦有一名乘客未能符合《預防及控制疾病規例》第599H，即未有病毒測試的陰性報告，或者在本港預訂酒店14晚的確認書。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署於是引同規例，禁止英航客機於今日起至本月25日期間由倫敦著陸香港。"},{"pid":"b8246e08b09d8496b2090bcdacd09ae52c5f75ea","tid":2322531,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:28:57.000Z","msg":"禁移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81968604cf2ed3316fa8d64f445e59dca92a28c7","tid":2322531,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:30:56.000Z","msg":"禁BA有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n駁機個班呢"},{"pid":"a59e021a8e0611ee34287ccdbef40d9e355d0430","tid":2322531,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:49:57.000Z","msg":"證明好多人移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"